               <msContents defective="false">
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1" defective="false">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donors; incipit of Texts I-1 and II; titles of books to be read; initial lines of prayers to be read; directive to the ministers; the abbreviations yәdi, bar ʾәgz (fols. 78r-79r); word “sälam” and its abbreviation in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
On the incipit pages of Texts I-1 and II (fols. 2r, 80r), few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
